channel.title: 317 Hecadi / Fally PvP/ Launched 26/11/14
channel.description:
[center]Home page: Hecadi.com Forums: Hecadi.com/forums[/center]
Hecadi is a server that has just launched, a lot of you may be thinking that it's not good enough or whatever, anyways i will be updating it daily because of my vacations, If you know me you know that there will be quality and unique updates, to be honest right now I haven't changed anything at all, but in this week i can be sure there will be alot of changes.
I already have a website running and just got the server running too.
Server Specs: Intel processor 1 core 2.8ghz 2gb Ram 512 video card It's not shared, or anything, the only thing running on the server is the game itself.
I'll be posting pictures real soon.
